-- Cognizant quarterly profit, revenue soar
-- 
-- Wed May 2, 2007 6:55am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/05/02/us-cognizant-results-idUSWNAS904820070502

 

 (Reuters) - Cognizant Technology Solutions Corp. ( CTSH.O ) reported a higher quarterly profit on a 61 percent increase in revenue from providing low-cost software development services in India. 

 First quarter net income rose to $75.4 million, or 50 cents per share, from $47.2 million, or 32 cents per share, a year earlier. Revenue climbed to $460.3 million from $285.5 million. (Reporting by Mathew Veedon in Bangalore)